{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-001", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [1]", "text_original": "惟三月，哉生魄，周公初基作新大邑于東國洛；四方民大和會，侯甸男邦采衛，百工播民，和見士于周？周公咸勤，乃洪大誥治。", "text_normalized": "惟三月，哉生魄，周公初基作新大邑于東國洛；四方民大和會，侯甸男邦采衛，百工播民，和見士于周？周公咸勤，乃洪大誥治。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-002", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [2]", "text_original": "王若曰：「孟侯，朕其弟，小子封。惟乃丕顯考文王，克明德慎罰，不敢侮鰥寡，庸庸、祗祗、威威、顯民。用肇造我區夏；越我一二邦，以修我西土。惟時怙，冒聞于上帝，帝休。天乃大命文王，殪戎殷，誕受厥命。越厥邦厥民，惟時敘。乃寡兄勖，肆汝小子封，在茲東土。」", "text_normalized": "王若曰：「孟侯，朕其弟，小子封。惟乃丕顯考文王，克明德慎罰，不敢侮鰥寡，庸庸、祗祗、威威、顯民。用肇造我區夏；越我一二邦，以修我西土。惟時怙，冒聞于上帝，帝休。天乃大命文王，殪戎殷，誕受厥命。越厥邦厥民，惟時敘。乃寡兄勖，肆汝小子封，在茲東土。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-003", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [3]", "text_original": "王曰：「嗚呼！封。汝念哉！今民將在祗遹乃文考，紹聞衣德言，往敷求于殷先哲王，用保乂民。汝丕遠惟商耇成人，宅心知訓。別求聞由古先哲王，用康保民，弘于天若。德裕乃身，不廢在王命。」", "text_normalized": "王曰：「嗚呼！封。汝念哉！今民將在祗遹乃文考，紹聞衣德言，往敷求于殷先哲王，用保乂民。汝丕遠惟商耇成人，宅心知訓。別求聞由古先哲王，用康保民，弘于天若。德裕乃身，不廢在王命。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-004", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [4]", "text_original": "王曰：「嗚呼！小子封。恫瘝乃身，敬哉！天畏棐忱，民情大可見。小人難保；往盡乃心，無康好逸豫，乃其乂民。我聞曰：『怨不在大，亦不在小；惠不惠，懋不懋。』", "text_normalized": "王曰：「嗚呼！小子封。恫瘝乃身，敬哉！天畏棐忱，民情大可見。小人難保；往盡乃心，無康好逸豫，乃其乂民。我聞曰：『怨不在大，亦不在小；惠不惠，懋不懋。』", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-005", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [5]", "text_original": "已，汝惟小子，乃服惟弘王，應保殷民；亦惟助王宅天命，作新民。」", "text_normalized": "已，汝惟小子，乃服惟弘王，應保殷民；亦惟助王宅天命，作新民。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-006", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [6]", "text_original": "王曰：「嗚呼！封。敬明乃罰。人有小罪非眚，乃惟終，自作不典；式爾，有厥罪小，乃不可不殺。乃有大罪非終，乃惟眚災適爾，既道極厥辜，時乃不可殺。」", "text_normalized": "王曰：「嗚呼！封。敬明乃罰。人有小罪非眚，乃惟終，自作不典；式爾，有厥罪小，乃不可不殺。乃有大罪非終，乃惟眚災適爾，既道極厥辜，時乃不可殺。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-007", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [7]", "text_original": "王曰：「嗚呼！封。有敘時，乃大明服，惟民其敕懋和。若有疾，惟民其畢棄咎。若保赤子，惟民其康乂。非汝封刑人殺人，無或刑人殺人；非汝封又曰劓刵人，無或劓刵人。」", "text_normalized": "王曰：「嗚呼！封。有敘時，乃大明服，惟民其敕懋和。若有疾，惟民其畢棄咎。若保赤子，惟民其康乂。非汝封刑人殺人，無或刑人殺人；非汝封又曰劓刵人，無或劓刵人。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-008", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [8]", "text_original": "王曰：「外事，汝陳時臬司，師茲殷罰有倫。」", "text_normalized": "王曰：「外事，汝陳時臬司，師茲殷罰有倫。」", "notes": ""}
