{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-013", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [13]", "text_original": "王曰：「封。元惡大憝，矧惟不孝不友。子弗祗服厥父事，大傷厥考心；于父不能字厥子，乃疾厥子。于弟弗念天顯，乃弗克恭厥兄；兄亦不念鞠子哀，大不友于弟。惟吊茲，不于我政人得罪；天惟與我民彝大泯亂；曰乃其速由文王作罰，刑茲無赦。", "text_normalized": "王曰：「封。元惡大憝，矧惟不孝不友。子弗祗服厥父事，大傷厥考心；于父不能字厥子，乃疾厥子。于弟弗念天顯，乃弗克恭厥兄；兄亦不念鞠子哀，大不友于弟。惟吊茲，不于我政人得罪；天惟與我民彝大泯亂；曰乃其速由文王作罰，刑茲無赦。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-014", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [14]", "text_original": "不率大戛，矧惟外庶子訓人、惟厥正人、越小臣、諸節，乃別播敷，造民大譽，弗念弗庸，瘝厥君；時乃引惡，惟朕憝。已，汝乃其速由茲義率殺。", "text_normalized": "不率大戛，矧惟外庶子訓人、惟厥正人、越小臣、諸節，乃別播敷，造民大譽，弗念弗庸，瘝厥君；時乃引惡，惟朕憝。已，汝乃其速由茲義率殺。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-015", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 15, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [15]", "text_original": "亦惟君惟長，不能厥家人、越厥小臣外正，惟威惟虐，大放王命：乃非德用乂。汝亦罔不克敬典，乃由裕民；惟文王之敬忌，乃裕民。曰：『我惟有及。』則予一人以懌。」", "text_normalized": "亦惟君惟長，不能厥家人、越厥小臣外正，惟威惟虐，大放王命：乃非德用乂。汝亦罔不克敬典，乃由裕民；惟文王之敬忌，乃裕民。曰：『我惟有及。』則予一人以懌。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-016", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 16, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [16]", "text_original": "王曰：「封！爽惟民，迪吉康。我時其惟殷先哲王德，用康乂民作求。矧今民罔迪不適，不迪則罔政在厥邦。」", "text_normalized": "王曰：「封！爽惟民，迪吉康。我時其惟殷先哲王德，用康乂民作求。矧今民罔迪不適，不迪則罔政在厥邦。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-017", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang", "source_id": "shangshu-039-zhou-shu-announcement-to-the-prince-of-kang__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 17, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 康誥 [17]", "text_original": "王曰：「封！予惟不可不監，告汝德之說，于罰之行。今惟民不靜，未戾厥心，迪屢未同。爽惟天其罰殛我，我其不怨。惟厥罪無在大，亦無在多，矧曰其尚顯聞于天。」", "text_normalized": "王曰：「封！予惟不可不監，告汝德之說，于罰之行。今惟民不靜，未戾厥心，迪屢未同。爽惟天其罰殛我，我其不怨。惟厥罪無在大，亦無在多，矧曰其尚顯聞于天。」", "notes": ""}
